-- Mexico Files Support of U.S. Court Order Blocking Arizona Immigration Law
-- B y   J o e l   R o s e n b l a t t
-- 2010-09-30T23:59:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/mexico-files-support-of-u-s-court-order-blocking-arizona-immigration-law.html
Mexico said it supports a U.S.
court ruling that blocks the central provisions of an Arizona
law requiring police to determine the immigration status of
people stopped for questioning, according to a court filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joel Rosenblatt in San Francisco at 
 jrosenblatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
